  "body": "It should be possible to prevent a hook from running.\n\nSpecifying `--disable-hooks` should prevent all hooks that would run on that command.\n\nFor example, `helm install --disable-hooks foo` would install foo, but would disable both the pre-install and post-install hooks (if they existed).\n",
